name: iter::range::<impl iter::traits::iterator::Iterator for ops::range::RangeInclusive<A>>::try_fold
src:
fn try_fold<B, F, R>(&mut self, init: B, f: F) -> R
    where
        Self: Sized,
        F: FnMut(B, Self::Item) -> R,
        R: Try<Output = B>,
    {
        self.spec_try_fold(init, f)
    }
